metadata.description: The Cuddly Reindeers collection consists of 9876 randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain, each one is completely unique. Cuddly Reindeer are exclusive, but there are some rarer than others. Each Cuddly Reindeer may include different fur, face, head accessory and attire - (and of course some special edition)
metadata.name: Cuddly Reindeer #1
